# UI/UX Standards

## Design Principles
- **ALWAYS** use dark-theme first approach
- **ALWAYS** enforce WCAG 2.2 AAA accessibility
- **ALWAYS** use enhanced-token or index.css for styling
- **NEVER** use hardcoded styles

## Documentation Standards
- **ALWAYS** consolidate documentation to reduce drift
- **NEVER** create overlapping README files
- **ALWAYS** maintain single source of truth (SSOT)
- **NEVER** create documentation without explicit request